Column one
About Us
Meet the Team at
Silver Lakes Realty, Inc.
Shelley Freshwater
is currently the Florida Licensed Real Estate Broker for Silver Lakes Realty, Inc.  Shelley has been a Broker in the Southwest Florida area for over 30 years and has always specialized in RV property sales and rentals. She is a mother of two (William 17 and Kate 16). Outside of family life and her real estate business, Shelley enjoys playing tennis and golf.
Robyn Jones
has been with Silver Lakes RV Resort for almost 25 years.  She graduated from Florida State University with her Master’s Degree in 2000. She is a Licensed Florida Realtor as well as an office manager and head of the rentals for Silver Lakes Realty, Inc. She is easy to work with and can accommodate any sales and rental needs you have. Robyn enjoys hanging out with her friends and family and watching Florida State football.
